    "comparability_notes": "This EPD is declared under PCR 2019:14 v2.0.1 (2025-06-05) and c-PCR-003 (2025-04-08). EPDs using earlier PCR versions (pre-v1.3) may use different GWP characterisation factors (IPCC AR6 with indirect radiative forcing vs IPCC AR5), which results in numerically different GWP-total values and limits direct comparability. Modules A4, A5 and B1-B7 are not declared; comparisons should be restricted to A1-A3 scope. The EPD covers a single plant at Rockbank, Victoria. The end-of-life scenario uses default PCR values (84% recycling, 16% landfill) based on Victorian NWR 2022 data. GWP-biogenic for A1-A3 is negative (-0.24 kg CO2-eq) due to proxy admixture data containing biogenic carbon."
